## 21Apr26 ‚Äî v0.3.3 addIcon format fix (blank icon)

- **Cause:** Obsidian `addIcon` expects **SVG fragment only** (no wrapping `<svg>`) and a **0 0 100 100** logical box; a full 18√ó18 `<svg>` string rendered empty.
- **Fix:** Inner `<g>` with paths in 0‚Äì100 coords + stroke-width 8 (same scale as Extended Graph‚Äôs custom icons). Ref: `obsidian-developer-docs` Icons.md.

