## 22Apr26 ‚Äî debug iteration: overlay/reticle path

- **Trigger:** User reports status text appears (`Graph select: lasso ...`) but there is still **no reticle / no selection effect**.
- **Evidence update:** H1‚ÄìH4 remain rejected: click, command dispatch, callback, and `setToolActive(true)` all occur. The prior host-selection refactor did **not** explain the missing reticle, so it was **reverted**.
